主义”问题</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3251436/chinas-protectionism-problem-local-levels-must-be-quelled-government-adviser-warns-beijing?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>著名政治学家郑永年表示，如果不解决地方官员中存在的问题，北京发展统一国内市场的计划将受到有效阻碍。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Feb 2024 02:00:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3251436/chinas-protectionism-problem-local-levels-must-be-quelled-government-adviser-warns-beijing?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国科技：5家美国风险投资公司在大陆人工智能、半导体领域投资超过30亿美元</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3251468/china-tech-five-us-venture-capital-firms-invested-over-us3-billion-mainland-ai-semiconductors?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>在对 GGV Capital、GSR Ventures、Qualcomm Ventures、Sequoia Capital 和 Walden International 进行调查后，众议院小组对“数十年的投资”表示遗憾。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 22:05:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3251468/china-tech-five-us-venture-capital-firms-invested-over-us3-billion-mainland-ai-semiconductors?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>随着加沙和红海冲突升级，中国在沙特防务展上展示无人机以吸引中东买家</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/military/article/3251429/china-spotlights-drones-saudi-defence-show-lure-middle-eastern-buyers-conflicts-gaza-and-red-sea?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>随着中东对无人战车的需求不断增长，北京的武器制造商在利雅得武器展上展示了无人机，中国的无人机已部署在也门内战和伊拉克。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 22:00:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/military/article/3251429/china-spotlights-drones-saudi-defence-show-lure-middle-eastern-buyers-conflicts-gaza-and-red-sea?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>世界需要中国在中东接受外交挑战</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/comment/opinion/article/3251390/world-needs-china-take-diplomatic-gauntlet-middle-east?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>中国有一个难得的机会来探索降低中东局势的选择，首先寻求结束暴力的升级并促成试探性谈判。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 21:30:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/comment/opinion/article/3251390/world-needs-china-take-diplomatic-gauntlet-middle-east?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国通胀：消费者价格跌幅创2009年以来最大幅度，1月份数据的4点启示</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/economic-indicators/article/3251373/china-inflation-4-takeaways-januarys-data-consumer-prices-suffered-steepest-fall-2009?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>由于担心通货紧缩风险，1月份中国消费者价格指数（CPI）连续第四个月下降，出厂价格也连续第16个月下降。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 16:00:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/economic-indicators/article/3251373/china-inflation-4-takeaways-januarys-data-consumer-prices-suffered-steepest-fall-2009?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国国家主席习近平与俄罗斯总统普京在农历新年前通电话誓言深化关系</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3251447/chinese-president-xi-jinping-russias-vladimir-putin-vow-deeper-ties-phone-call-ahead-lunar-new-year?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>据央视报道，中国国家主席习近平向俄罗斯总统普京表示，两国必须“坚决反对”外部干涉，坚称需要捍卫主权、安全和发展利益。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 14:08:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3251447/chinese-president-xi-jinping-russias-vladimir-putin-vow-deeper-ties-phone-call-ahead-lunar-new-year?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>尽管面临IPO挑战和双边摩擦，中国初创企业仍然渴望美国投资者</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/money-wealth/article/3251427/market-call-chinese-start-ups-still-crave-us-investors-despite-ipo-challenges-bilateral-friction?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>中国的首次公开募股一度获得了印钞许可，但由于财务不透明、丑闻以及滴滴出行于 2022 年在纽约证券交易所突然退市而蒙上了阴影。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 14:00:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/money-wealth/article/3251427/market-call-chinese-start-ups-still-crave-us-investors-despite-ipo-challenges-bilateral-friction?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国国家主席习近平在农历新年前的讲话中赞扬香港和澳门一体化取得的进展</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3251445/chinas-xi-jinping-hails-progress-integrating-hong-kong-and-macau-speech-ahead-lunar-new-year?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>在庆祝农历新年的年度国家聚会上，中国领导人还赞扬北京在反对“台独”和“外国势力干涉”方面取得的成功。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 13:29:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3251445/chinas-xi-jinping-hails-progress-integrating-hong-kong-and-macau-speech-ahead-lunar-new-year?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>量子突破：中国科学家用新模拟器解决了20年的物理争论</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/science/article/3251440/quantum-breakthrough-chinese-scientists-settle-20-year-physics-debate-new-simulator?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>中国科学技术大学的研究人员使用强大的量子模拟器，依靠高质量气体来可视化可以揭示超导体机制的现象，这是“非凡且令人兴奋”的突破。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 13:00:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/science/article/3251440/quantum-breakthrough-chinese-scientists-settle-20-year-physics-debate-new-simulator?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中概股下滑、美股下滑——改革能阻止潮流吗？</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3251431/china-stocks-slide-us-stocks-glide-will-reform-work-stem-tide?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>美国和中国正走在不同的经济道路上，各自的股市就是例证。在中国试图化解危机之际，专家们主张进行广泛的改革，以解决拖累经济增长和复苏前景的根本性问题。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 12:30:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3251431/china-stocks-slide-us-stocks-glide-will-reform-work-stem-tide?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国最高立法机构将讨论军队清洗中的“任免”</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3251425/chinas-top-legislative-body-discuss-appointments-and-dismissals-amid-military-purge?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>在高级将领和前国防部长李尚孚被免职后，全国人民代表大会常务委员会发出了进一步改组的信号。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 10:03:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3251425/chinas-top-legislative-body-discuss-appointments-and-dismissals-amid-military-purge?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国科学家利用斯特林发动机冷却技术打造强大的微波武器，可以从移动的卡车上发射</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/science/article/3251381/chinese-scientists-build-powerful-stirling-engine-based-microwave-weapon-can-fire-moving-truck?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>这种高威力武器系统可以从移动的卡车上发射，并且仅使用现有方法的五分之一的能量。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 10:00:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/science/article/3251381/chinese-scientists-build-powerful-stirling-engine-based-microwave-weapon-can-fire-moving-truck?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item></channel></rss>